00:34:08,799 --> 00:34:11,552
<i>dengan cita-cita, dan saya syak, emosi.</i>

432
00:34:15,097 --> 00:34:16,098
<i>Tommy Molto.</i>

433
00:34:17,224 --> 00:34:19,351
<i>Dia sengaja abaikan elemen tertentu
